helpdesk_ticket.description_html:
On Wed, 17 Dec, 2025, 21:48 Sandhya Nackwal, <grievance-officer@pharmeasy.in> wrote:
Hello,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

With regards to your order #657384958671097856-30119, I am sorry to know that you have received medicines in a damaged condition. Please accept my sincere apologies for the inconvenience caused.

Kindly share the images of that product with the batch number (MRP details) for further action.

Awaiting your response.

Regards,
Sandhya Nackwal
